on and yoga practices. Our expert facilitators guide you on a journey of self-discovery and inner peace.</p>\n        </section>\n\n        <section id=\"offerings\" class=\"section\">\n            <h3>Our Offerings</h3>\n            <img src=\"https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1544405194-956077550c7e?ixlib=rb-1.2.1&auto=format&fit=crop&w=1350&q=80\" alt=\"Yoga Pose\">\n            <p>We offer a range of retreats tailored to different needs, from weekend getaways focused on mindfulness to week-long deep dives into yoga philosophy. Our programs include daily meditation sessions, dynamic and restorative yoga classes, nourishing organic meals, and opportunities for quiet reflection amidst nature.</p>\n        </section>\n\n        <section id=\"gallery\" class=\"section\">\n            <h3>Gallery</h3>\n            <img src=\"https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1489533119213-6bb6c175a260?ixlib=rb-1.2.1&auto=format&fit=crop&w=1350&q=80\" alt=\"Meditation Space\">\n            <p>Immerse yourself in the beauty of our retreat center. Explore our serene meditation gardens, comfortable accommodation, and the breathtaking natural surroundings that inspire peace and tranquility.</p>\n        </section>\n\n        <section id=\"contact\" class=\"section\">\n            <h3>Connect With Us</h3>\n            <p>Ready to embark on your journey to inner peace? We'd love to hear from you.</p>\n            <p>\n                <strong>Email:</strong> info@serenehavenretreats.com<br>\n                <strong>Phone:</strong> (123) 456-7890\n            </p>\n            <a href=\"#\" class=\"cta-button\">Book Your Retreat</a>\n        </section>\n    </div>\n\n    <footer>\n        <p>&copy; 2023 Serene Haven Retreats. All rights reserved.</p>\n        <p><a href=\"#\">Privacy Policy</a> | <a href=\"#\">Terms of Service</a></p>\n    </footer>\n</body>\n</html>\n```"}